query:
SELECT pr.id, pr.questionId, q.questionKey, pr.value, pr.comment, pr.responseId, pr.updatedAt 
FROM partnerResponses pr
JOIN questions q ON pr.questionId = q.id
WHERE pr.partnerQuestionnaireId = 1
ORDER BY pr.updatedAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
